-- Saudi Cement Sales Rise 17% in the First Half of 2010, Eqtisadiah Reports
-- Mourad Haroutunian
-- 2010-07-17T06:05:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-17/saudi-cement-sales-rise-17-in-the-first-half-of-2010-eqtisadiah-reports.html

          
          
             The volume of Saudi cement producers
grew 17 percent to 22.1 million tons in the first half of 2010
on higher demand, Al Eqtisadiah reported, citing the Ministry of
Commerce and Industry.  
